#define IHaveSubdirs

     TESTDATA = 
    DATAFILES = README amiga ataritt chicony dell everex fujitsu keytronic \
		kinesis macintosh microsoft nec northgate pc sony \
		sun winbook \
		$(TESTDATA)
      SUBDIRS = digital hp ibm sgi

all::

MakeXkbDir($(LIBDIR)/xkb,geometry)
InstallMultiple($(DATAFILES),$(LIBDIR)/xkb/geometry)
DependSubdirs($(SUBDIRS))
